  "texts": [
    "In contrast, Figure 12 shows that monetary-fiscal coordination does not show strong differences between crisis and non-crisis times and advanced and non-advanced (developing and emerging) countries.",
    "This can point towards fiscal-monetary interactions taking place both in normal and in crisis times and being less controversial in communication.",
